column5: Hey guys. Gonna head out to couch tmrw morning, just wondering what the walking conditions were like. Thanks in advance! Tight lines
I’m gonna assume that it won’t be easy with the recent storm snow.
Walking conditions weren’t too bad, maybe 3” of snow. We had a decent day, lots of little ones with a few jumbos
Nice catch!! The same results as I am having, lots of throw backs but a few keepers But its great to get out Are you going out from Tudhope?
I run a 4 wheeler So do a little traveling Getting on in the Cumberland Beach area
